name: CryptoSerpent #005
description: Jim Eatsalot escaped in the police ship L-101 with a group of inmates. He saved his best friend Elliot from a swordfish attack with a lipstick and a mirror. He fantasizes about escaping from jail and living a new life as a transerpent. After landing, he got carried away with his impulses and ate a half dozen hamsters at a local California pet store. He says he has no regrets.
